---
title: Creamy Garlic Chicken Breasts with Potatoes and Parmesan
description: Tonight's twist on a meat-and-potatoes dinner is rich, creamy and speedy! We've snuck some spinach into the sauce... the kids won't even notice!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-garlic-chicken-breasts-3bdc732f.jpg
